txt.en: Do your part in the battle. Slay the Free People where they are found and earn your place in the army of Angmar!
Battle in the Ettenmoors rages! You are called to slaughter the enemy in great numbers.
Make your way into the Ettenmoors and slaughter all the Free People you find.
Brag to War-tyrant Akúlhun of your glorious efforts
'Look who has returned. Well, [placeholder], if only every warrior was as proficient as you we'd soon wipe this world clean of these disgusting cretins.'
